front.title: H'nemthe
front.gametext: Adds 2 to power of anything she pilots. Adds 2 to deploy cost of each opponent's male Imperial when that Imperial is deploying to same or adjacent site.
front.lore: Starfaring explorers. H'nemthe have a reputation for being sly and unforgiving. Many abandoned their homeworld after the Empire invaded. The females ritually kill their males.

pulledBy: Nar Shaddaa Wind Chimes & Out Of Somewhere
